        public void printPath(java.lang.String destName)

      • dijkstra

        public void dijkstra(java.lang.String startName,
                     int numVertices,
                     int numEdges)
        Single-source weighted shortest-path algorithm. (Dijkstra) using priority queues based on the binary heap then prints number of Vertices and Edges and counts for number of operations for Vertices, Edges and Prioroty Queue
        Parameters:
        numVertices - - Number of vertices in the file.
        numEdges - - Number of edges in the file.
